        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <h3>Do you deliver and set up?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yes! We handle full delivery, professional setup and pickup after
              your event. You don't have to worry about a thing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <h3>How early should I book?</h3>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              We recommend booking at least 2 weeks before your event date to
              ensure availability. For peak seasons, book even earlier.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item reveal">
          <button class="faq-question">
            <h3>Do you offer customized event packages?</h3>
